= Other Positions

I worked as a grader for CMSC/MATH475: Combinatorics and Graph Theory my senior year
of undergrad. Previous to that, I spent two semesters as a teaching assistant for CMSC250: Discrete 
Structures. I also worked as a math coach in the 
[http://reslife.umd.edu/mathsuccess/ Math Success Program] at UMD. 
